Title: Object: The Ostrich
Description: An ostrich running with wings half-spread, from right to left across open ground, another running in the background to left, and a mounted man in a turban chasing them with dogs; from a series. 1741 Etching and engraving
Curator's comments: See also 1914,0520.483, 485 and 486, which appear to be from the same series, despite differences in lettering: in this impression the separate platemark for the letterpress inscription clear in 483 and 485, is not visible.
